Worked well in version: 1.75.0
Bug in version: 1.76.0

I use Vue 3 (sass) in combination with tailwind. Code block that's causing error:

```
<style lang="scss" scoped>
@keyframes shake {
  10%,
  90% {
    @apply -translate-x-px;
  }

  20%,
  80% {
    @apply translate-x-0.5;
  }

  30%,
  50%,
  70% {
    @apply -translate-x-1;
  }

  40%,
  60% {
    @apply translate-x-1;
  }
}
</style>
```

